mina Elias","date":"October 3, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik\u00a0reported: The\u00a0Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever is pleased to have his provision expanded and his life span extended, let him keep good relations with his family.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2067, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2557 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33332,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/02\/relations-with-deceased-parents\/","url_meta":{"origin":1028,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Parents: How to maintain relations with deceased parents?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 2, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever would like to maintain relations with his father in his grave, let him maintain relations with his father\u2019s brothers after him.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 432 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Suyuti \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19119,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/12\/maintain-relations-kuffar-family\/","url_meta":{"origin":1028,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Family: The Prophet does not cut off unbelieving relatives","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 12, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"'Amr ibn al-\u2018As reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the relatives\u00a0of my father are not my allies. Verily, only Allah and the righteous believers are my allies. Yet, they have the bonds of kinship and I will uphold their family ties.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5990,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/09\/13\/compensate-father\/","url_meta":{"origin":1028,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Parents: No child can truly repay his father","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 13, 2010","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira\u00a0reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo child can repay his father unless he finds him as a slave, purchases him, and emanicaptes him.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u00a0Muslim 1510 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1040,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/09\/21\/be-good-family\/","url_meta":{"origin":1028,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Rahim: Be good to family, even if they are not","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 21, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: A man said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, I have relatives with whom I try to relate but they cut me off. I treat them well, but they treat me badly. I am forbearing with them, but they are harsh with me.\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":459,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/01\/28\/womb-rahm-mercy-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":1028,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Rahim: The womb is derived from mercy of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 28, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Verily, the womb derives its name from the Merciful. Allah said: I will keep good relations with one who keeps good relations with your relatives, and I will sever relations with one who severs relations with your relatives.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1028","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"c